{"tid":2251842,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟不才 P牌仔有野想徵求意見","createTime":"2020-10-21T05:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T18:23:06.000Z","uid":257695,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a4636009286a03f8ae5a9ab61a8a7626a33f80ce","tid":2251842,"uid":257695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T05:28:32.000Z","msg":"08 年Corolla 腳車 番工番學用 屋企人之前揸開無問題<br />\n而家揸長途冷氣時有時無 大約有70%時間有冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早兩日去左車房睇 佢話冷氣泵散左 d碎入左個散熱同哇佬要換冷氣泵 散熱網 同哇佬 報價以上冷氣野加消耗品  <br />\n都要10k以上（四千幾整冷氣+5千幾消耗品）<br />\n用番日本仔野要成14k（八千幾整冷氣加5千幾消耗品）<br />\n牌費到下年3月<br />\n<br />\n咁既情況大家有咩意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身下年4月甩p想換車<br />\n但係又唔知50k-100k 買第二架車番黎洗唔洗整<br />\n屋企人用 心機車 但架車只值20-30k <br />\n拎10-15k黎維修又好似無咩意義<br />\nSor for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴打可以幫手分析下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c616cecb6b05a14c814dd501b548d0a93b7071","tid":2251842,"uid":141148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"劏咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f626ff1d22692f8ce27c97cc89561de4b05e9aa","tid":2251842,"uid":257695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76c616cecb6b05a14c814dd501b548d0a93b7071","tid":2251842,"uid":141148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"劏咗佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T05:36:45.000Z","msg":"淨係壞冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似好浪費"},{"pid":"09edccfaf5d910c5aba14082b10e5f56063c53b8","tid":2251842,"uid":264290,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8f626ff1d22692f8ce27c97cc8956